---
title: Autumn Applesauce Pork with Roasted Green Beans and Baby Potatoes
description: Raise your hand if you’ve tasted a better pairing than pork and apples. Yeah, we thought so. There’s just something about this family-friendly, sweet-and-savory combination that keeps us coming back again and again. In this recipe, homemade applesauce pairs with juicy seared pork tenderloin and a side of roasted green beans for a meal that’ll make the everyone smile.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/autumn-applesauce-pork-fa98e5d8.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/autumn-applesauce-pork-ad670010.pdf
time required: 40 minutes
servings: 2
cuisine: North America
